{
  "doc_id": "30677",
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] a method is introduced for answering several types of textual questions grounded with images while [CITATION_2] proposes the task of open-ended visual question answering. In another recent approach [CITATION_3] , knowledge extracted from web visual data is used to answer open-domain questions. While these works all use visual reasoning to answer questions, none have considered solving analogy questions.",
